</div>

## ‚ú® Features

- **üéÆ Intuitive Remote Interface**: Clean, modern UI with familiar remote control layout
- **‚å®Ô∏è Keyboard Shortcuts**: Full keyboard navigation support for quick control
- **üåà System Theme Integration**: Automatically adapts to your system's light/dark theme
- **üîß Easy Setup Wizard**: Step-by-step configuration with automatic entity discovery
- **üì± Multiple Remote Support**: Manage and switch between multiple Home Assistant remotes
- **üîí Secure Authentication**: Uses Home Assistant's long-lived access tokens
- **üñ•Ô∏è Cross-Platform**: Works on Windows, macOS, and Linux
- **‚ö° Responsive Design**: Fast, non-blocking command execution

